  • Constructor Details

    • Pet

      public Pet(String difficulty, int healthVal, int sleepVal, int fullnessVal, int happinessVal, int maxHealth, int maxSleep, int maxFullness, int maxHappiness, int healthLoss, int sleepLoss, int fullnessLoss, int happinessLoss, int healthGain, int sleepGain, int fullnessGain, int happinessGain, int pieCount, int bananaCount, int pizzaCount, int ballCount, int plushCount, int swordCount, String name, int score)
      Constructor for the Pet class. Initializes a virtual pet with specified attributes, inventory counts, loss and gain rates, and game difficulty level.
      Parameters:
      difficulty - The difficulty level of the game.
      healthVal - Initial health value.
      sleepVal - Initial sleep value.
      fullnessVal - Initial fullness value.
      happinessVal - Initial happiness value.
      maxHealth - Maximum health value.
      maxSleep - Maximum sleep value.
      maxFullness - Maximum fullness value.
      maxHappiness - Maximum happiness value.
      healthLoss - Rate of health decrease over time.
      sleepLoss - Rate of sleep decrease over time.
      fullnessLoss - Rate of fullness decrease over time.
      happinessLoss - Rate of happiness decrease over time.
      healthGain - Amount of health gained from actions or items.
      sleepGain - Amount of sleep gained from actions or items.
      fullnessGain - Amount of fullness gained from actions or items.
      happinessGain - Amount of happiness gained from actions or items.
      pieCount - Initial number of pies in the inventory.
      bananaCount - Initial number of bananas in the inventory.
      pizzaCount - Initial number of pizzas in the inventory.
      ballCount - Initial number of balls in the inventory.
      plushCount - Initial number of plush toys in the inventory.
      swordCount - Initial number of swords in the inventory.
      name - The name of the pet.
      score - The starting score for the pet.
